Class Relationship

java.lang.Object
CsvToJsonConverter.BaseEntity
CsvToJsonConverter.Relationship
class Relationship extends BaseEntity
Represents a relationship between two entities (Subject and Object) with a specific Type. Includes fields identifying the subject, object, their types, and potentially a related number (IdNum).
